<section class="pc-about-hero">
  <div class="pc-container">
    <h1 class="pc-about-title">About <%= site && site.broker && site.broker.full_name || 'Our Real Estate Team' %></h1>
    <p class="pc-about-sub">Trusted local partner for buying, selling and renting properties. We combine on‑ground expertise with data‑driven insights to help you make confident decisions.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="pc-container pc-about-wrap">
  <div class="pc-about-card">
    <h2 style="margin-top:0">Our Story</h2>
    <p>Since day one, our focus has been simple—deliver honest advice and close smoothly. Over the years we have built a strong network of owners, developers and financial institutions across the city. That network allows us to surface the right options faster, negotiate better and protect you at every step.</p>
    <ul class="pc-about-bullets">
      <li>End‑to‑end help for buy, sell, rent and investment</li>
      <li>On‑ground team for property discovery and due diligence</li>
      <li>Clear documentation with RERA‑compliant processes</li>
      <li>Dedicated relationship manager until possession</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="pc-stats">
      <div class="pc-stat"><div class="pc-stat-num">10+ yrs</div><div class="pc-stat-label">Experience</div></div>
      <div class="pc-stat"><div class="pc-stat-num">1200+</div><div class="pc-stat-label">Homes Closed</div></div>
      <div class="pc-stat"><div class="pc-stat-num">25+</div><div class="pc-stat-label">Localities Covered</div></div>
      <div class="pc-stat"><div class="pc-stat-num">4.9/5</div><div class="pc-stat-label">Client Rating</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="pc-about-cta">
      <a class="pc-btn pc-btn-primary" href="<%= nav && nav.properties || '#' %>">Browse Properties</a>
      <a class="pc-btn pc-btn-light" href="<%= nav && nav.contact || '#' %>">Talk to an Expert</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pc-about-card">
    <img class="pc-about-image" src="/templates/proclassic/public/img/placeholder.jpg" alt="Our office" />
    <div class="pc-about-gallery">
      <img class="pc-about-thumb" src="/templates/proclassic/public/img/placeholder.jpg" alt="Team" />
      <img class="pc-about-thumb" src="/templates/proclassic/public/img/placeholder.jpg" alt="Site visit" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="pc-container pc-values-wrap">
  <h2 class="pc-section__title pc-center">Our Values</h2>
  <div class="pc-values">
    <div class="pc-value">
      <h3 style="margin-top:0">Transparency</h3>
      <p>No surprises. From property titles to payment schedules, you always know what is happening and why.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pc-value">
      <h3 style="margin-top:0">Local Expertise</h3>
      <p>Street‑level knowledge of projects, developers and micro‑markets so you get the complete picture.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pc-value">
      <h3 style="margin-top:0">Clients First</h3>
      <p>Your goals drive every decision. We negotiate hard on your behalf and stay with you beyond possession.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>



